headline: GTA Online
subtitle: Business Fleet
content: Once your Warehouse is operational you’ll be shifting unprecedented levels of product, so you’re going to need some serious transportation. That’s why you’ll find the new and exclusive model of the Vapid Speedo waiting in the garage below the nightclub - and if that’s not enough, you’ll also have exclusive purchase options on custom editions of the Maibatsu Mule and the MTL Pounder. Once you’ve seen the mod options on these three, you’ll never use anything else.
